    "display_name": "E.R. Doctor",
    "long_instructions": "## Dr. Maria Gonzalez, Emergency Room Doctor\r\n\r\n**Location:** Juba, South Sudan\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Juba Teaching Hospital\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Emergency medicine, toxicology, snakebite treatment\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"In South Sudan, where snakebites are common and medical resources are limited, the AI Snake Identification App helps us quickly determine if a bite is from a venomous snake. This technology speeds up diagnosis, reduces misidentification, and ensures patients get the right antivenom in time.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
